Date: Jan 15, 29
Lines: orth orth-seg gloss translat
Source a: Hixkaryana and Linguistic Typology: Desmond C Derbyshire

#1 Word order trans

Source: a
Vetted: t
Judgment: g
Phenomena: {word order}
toto yonono kamara
toto y-ono-no kamara
person 3sg-eat-past jaguar
`The jaguar ate the person.'

